title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1983-05-14
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Friend Of The Devil, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Tennessee Jed, My Brother Esau-> Bertha

Set 2

Shakedown Street, Playin' In The Band-> China Doll-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Playin' In The Band-> Morning Dew-> Sugar Magnolia, E: One More Saturday Night

reviews.review_text: love me some 83 great sound for an audience fob imo. bobby could be a  bit louder but brent, phil, and jer are mixed very well, thank you sir mick. the boys sound like they're havin fun tonight.
